Da Hae, can I have a word with you?

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.270
- Okay.
- Good work, everyone.

00:14:37.340 --> 00:14:39.010
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:43.580
Why the long face?

00:14:46.150 --> 00:14:50.450
I wonder if dropping this business
is really the best for everyone.

00:14:53.490 --> 00:14:56.430
