- Why not discuss it with friends?
- What?

00:15:03.870 --> 00:15:07.600
When you're chatting with friends,
sometimes ideas just start flowing.

00:15:07.970 --> 00:15:11.670
That group you always hang out with.
That crew of off-cycle hires...

00:15:13.580 --> 00:15:15.880
I mean, your besties.

00:15:16.110 --> 00:15:17.480
Talk it over with them.

00:15:18.010 --> 00:15:20.920
Conversation is the solution
to all our problems.

00:15:20.980 --> 00:15:21.980
Okay?

00:15:22.550 --> 00:15:23.690
Take your time.

00:15:25.990 --> 00:15:26.990
A conversation...

00:15:31.290 --> 00:15:32.290
You're working late?

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:36.270
Yes. I have to work late.
Help me brainstorm a bit,

00:15:37.400 --> 00:15:38.570
and we can keep an eye
on our crypto.

00:15:38.970 --> 00:15:41.370
We can watch the charts live
and make some moves together.

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:43.810
Ta-da!

00:15:44.440 --> 00:15:46.010
I even brought snacks!

00:15:46.010 --> 00:15:48.740
I've got tteokbokki,
fish cake soup, and sundae.

00:15:48.810 --> 00:15:49.810
Looks delicious, right?

00:15:49.950 --> 00:15:52.250
Should we book a conference room?

00:15:52.310 --> 00:15:53.520
We could use the big screen...

00:15:53.580 --> 00:15:55.420
- No way.
- What?

00:15:55.480 --> 00:15:57.950
- What?
- Is crypto a soccer match?

00:15:58.250 --> 00:16:00.760
Why would you all gather around
just to watch it?

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:04.530
Why not? This is as big
as the Korea-Japan match to us.

00:16:05.030 --> 00:16:06.500
I'm just tired.

00:16:07.860 --> 00:16:10.170
I'm heading out. Enjoy.

