She's been leaving work later, too.

00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:34.460
Why?

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:37.130
Is the Sales Team that busy
these days?

00:16:38.260 --> 00:16:39.490
It seems that way.

00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:41.630
She doesn't discuss work in detail.

00:16:41.630 --> 00:16:42.660
True.

00:16:42.660 --> 00:16:45.430
- Okay, I'll set the 1-minute chart.
- Okay.

00:16:46.900 --> 00:16:48.770
Alright, let's pray.

00:16:49.740 --> 00:16:50.770
Okay, fine.

00:16:52.610 --> 00:16:54.140
Okay. Dear deities.

00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:57.110
If the crypto goes up,
I swear I'll be a better person.

00:16:57.180 --> 00:17:00.620
I'll take every flyer
from the old ladies on the street.

00:17:00.680 --> 00:17:02.150
And trash...

00:17:02.150 --> 00:17:04.850
