It dropped.

00:17:17.100 --> 00:17:18.100
Darn it.

00:17:18.930 --> 00:17:20.170
Dear deities!

00:17:20.340 --> 00:17:23.940
If this crypto goes up,
I'll be good.

00:17:23.940 --> 00:17:25.070
I'll even stop losing my temper.

00:17:25.140 --> 00:17:26.710
Also, I'll stop drinking...

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:29.280
You're going to stop?

00:17:32.710 --> 00:17:35.020
I'll stick to domestic beer.

00:17:35.820 --> 00:17:38.390
Please, just five percent!

00:17:38.390 --> 00:17:40.020
- Just five percent!
- Just five percent!

00:17:42.860 --> 00:17:43.890
It dropped.

00:17:44.130 --> 00:17:45.160
Darn it.

00:17:48.430 --> 00:17:50.670
Dear deities!

00:17:50.670 --> 00:17:52.670
- Dear deities!
- Dear deities!

00:17:53.040 --> 00:17:56.240
- Dear deities!
- Dear deities!

00:17:56.240 --> 00:17:59.910
- Please, just five percent!
- Just five percent, please!

00:18:10.820 --> 00:18:11.890
Did it go up?

00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:15.290
No.

00:18:15.560 --> 00:18:16.760
No!

00:18:16.830 --> 00:18:17.930
(Please go up one percent.)

00:18:23.500 --> 00:18:25.000
What's this?

00:18:25.270 --> 00:18:27.740
Did you see the crypto
dropped again...

