Yes, ma'am.

00:18:31.410 --> 00:18:34.240
I was calling to see if anyone
was interested in renting my place.

00:18:35.080 --> 00:18:37.950
I see. Please handle it
as soon as possible.

00:18:38.010 --> 00:18:39.380
It's pretty urgent.

00:18:39.950 --> 00:18:42.150
- Okay.
- What was that?

00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:45.220
Her apartment...

00:18:45.590 --> 00:18:46.960
She's putting it on the market?

00:18:47.860 --> 00:18:49.020
This is huge.

00:18:49.020 --> 00:18:50.890
Did you see Hoppang Bite's post?

00:18:51.090 --> 00:18:53.700
A coworker made a million dollars.

00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:55.300
They hit it big with crypto.

00:18:55.860 --> 00:18:57.200
It was called Enderion, I think?

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:59.800
But didn't that crash recently?

00:18:59.870 --> 00:19:01.740
They must've cashed out at the peak.

00:19:01.940 --> 00:19:03.340
You know it's all about timing.

00:19:03.410 --> 00:19:04.710
I'm so jealous.

00:19:05.210 --> 00:19:08.210
Who could it be?
You read the post and have no idea?

00:19:08.280 --> 00:19:09.680
